14:34
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='863790' id='t-863790'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:39
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='868541' id='t-868541'>Today, it is no longer a question</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='870614' id='t-870614'>of if change is possible.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='873422' id='t-873422'>The question is not, &quot;Can we?&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='876367' id='t-876367'>The question is, &quot;Will we?&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
